    antwoord: "Nulpunten: x³-3x = 0 → x(x²-3) = 0 → x=0, x=±√3. f'(x) = 3x²-3 = 3(x²-1). Extremen: f'(x)=0 → x=±1. f(1)=1-3=-2 (minimum), f(-1)=-1+3=2 (maximum). f''(x) = 6x. Buigpunt: f''(x)=0 → x=0, f(0)=0. Buigpunt: (0,0)."
