    antwoord: "(a) y = x³ → x = y³ → y = x^(1/3) = ∛x. Inverse: f⁻¹(x) = x^(1/3), domein: ℝ. (b) y = 3·ln(x) + 2 → y - 2 = 3·ln(x) → ln(x) = (y-2)/3 → x = e^((y-2)/3). Inverse: g⁻¹(x) = e^((x-2)/3), domein: ℝ."
