    antwoord: "Stap 1: y = (x+2)/(x-1) → y(x-1) = x+2 → yx - y = x + 2 → yx - x = y + 2 → x(y-1) = y+2 → x = (y+2)/(y-1). Inverse: f⁻¹(x) = (x+2)/(x-1) = f(x). Bewijs: f(f(x)) = f((x+2)/(x-1)) = ((x+2)/(x-1) + 2) / ((x+2)/(x-1) - 1) = ((x+2+2(x-1))/(x-1)) / ((x+2-(x-1))/(x-1)) = (3x)/(3) = x. Dus f(f(x)) = x, wat bevestigt dat f⁻¹ = f."
