    antwoord: "R·sin(x+φ) = R·sin(x)·cos(φ) + R·cos(x)·sin(φ). Vergelijk: R·cos(φ) = 3 en R·sin(φ) = 3. R² = 9+9 = 18 → R = 3√2. tan(φ) = 3/3 = 1 → φ = π/4. Dus 3sin(x) + 3cos(x) = 3√2·sin(x + π/4)."
